<article style="max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; padding-top: 2rem;">
    <header style="margin-bottom: 3rem; text-align: center;">
        <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; letter-spacing: -0.5px;">About Qalam</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="post-content" style="font-size: 1.15rem;">
        <p>In an era of digital clutter, the core focus of human-computer interaction should be reducing cognitive load. Qalam was built with a singular purpose: to provide a serene, distraction-free environment for writers and thinkers.</p>
        
        <p>By utilizing carefully constrained line lengths, unbleached color palettes, and elegant typography, we prioritize the reader's focus and the writer's flow above all else.</p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">The Architecture</h3>
        <p>This platform operates on a robust MVC architecture powered by Node.js and Express. Content is securely managed within MongoDB, with media handled seamlessly via custom middleware, ensuring a lightweight and responsive experience from draft to publication.</p>
    </div>
</article>

